## Commit Conventions

- Types: `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `refactor:`, `chore:`
- Imperative mood, lowercase first letter, max 72 char subject
- HEREDOC format, always include co-author line
- Co-author: `{{CO_AUTHOR}} <noreply@anthropic.com>`

